No. 11-363 (R46-005). Amgen Inc., Petitioner v. New York, et al. 565 U.S. 1103, 132 S. Ct. 993,

181 L. Ed. 2d 570,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 9021. December 27, 2011.

The petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the First Circuit in the above-entitled case was dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 652 F.3d 103.
